  "text": "Addition of 3xFLAG tag to ycjW at its chromosomal locus was achieved as previously described, with slight modifications [CITATION_1] . Briefly, primers pLL14 and pLL15 were used to PCR amplify Cm R cassette from pKD4. PCR product was transformed into appropriate electrocompetent strains.",
